  "_comment": [
    "Optional sidecars the desktop app can lazy-download after install.",
    "Each component is keyed by id. The manifest is embedded in the app via",
    "include_str! at compile time so a user with no network still sees the",
    "full menu of optional components and can choose to skip them.",
    "",
    "Per-triple URLs point at GitHub Releases (or any static host). SHA256",
    "MUST match or install aborts. Update current_version to roll out a new",
    "build; the auto-updater reruns install on next launch."
  ],
